ActCanadian Environmental Assessment Act, 2012
SubjectLaurentia Project: Port of Quebec Deep-Water Wharf - Beauport Sector, in Quebec City
PrecisOrder deciding that the significant adverse environmental effects that the LAURENTIA PROJECT: PORT OF QUEBEC DEEP-WATER WHARF - BEAUPORT SECTOR, proposed by the Quebec Port Authority (QPA), in Quebec City, is likely to cause are not justified in the circumstances.
